response.overview: December 3rd, 2011 :: Combat Zone Wrestling presents Cage Of Death 13 from the Asylum Arena in Philadelphia, PA, USA. Matches include:  • CZW World Heavyweight Title Cage Of Death Match Devon Moore (c) vs. MASADA vs. Robert Anthony vs. Scotty Vortekz  • CZW Wired TV Title Match Jake Crist (c) vs. Dave Crist  • Best 2 Out Of 3 Tables Match The Runaways & Kimber Lee vs. BLK OUT  • #1 Contendership Scramble Match Derek Frazier vs. tHURTeen vs. Drew Gulak vs. Alex Payne vs. Ryan McBride vs. Dustin Rayz  • 4 Corners Of Pain Match Drake Younger vs. Rory Mondo  • Jaki Numazawa, Jun Kasai, Kamui, Masahiro Takanashi & Yoshihito Sasaki vs. Danshoku Dino, Kengo Mashimo, KUDO, Ryuji Ito & Takashi Sasaki  • Eddie Kingston & Homicide vs. Philly's Most Wanted  • CZW Junior Heavyweight Title Match Sami Callihan (c) vs. AR Fox  • Ultraviolent Pits Match Danny Havoc vs. Matt Tremont  • No Holds Barred Match DJ Hyde vs. Greg Excellent
response.title: CZW Cage Of Death XIII
